title: What does the application management screen look like?
answer:
On the application management screen, you can switch between the following three tabs: Downloaded, Running, and All. 

 ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=113081)![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=113082) ![](http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=113083)

 Applications are displayed in the center. 

 Storage information is displayed at the bottom of the screen.
